author: H
title: H
text: I have used this site twice before , it's now my third time ordering and it's been good. Shipping can be slow sometimes but it's nothing that isn't already stated, every item has a shipped by date besides it which gives you a general idea of how long it will take. Also all items I have ordered so far seem genuine although I wouldn't be 100% sure, I still get all the asian products I otherwise don't find in normal stores so I'm satisfied.
